    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Code-heavy PCF change adding new ListView + SortableColumns components, selection/sort/pin state, localStorage persistence; modifies production SemanticSearchControl; ADR-021 + ADR-022 binding; depends on FR-BFF-01 projection</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
