    <patterns>
      <pattern name="Fluent v9 DataGrid/Table" location=".claude/patterns/ui/fluent-v9-component-authoring.md">
        Use Fluent v9 `DataGrid` or `Table` primitives for column-row layouts; semantic header role for sortable columns.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="localStorage scoping" location="src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl.tsx">
        Key pattern: `spaarke.docs.{feature}.{userId}.{matterId}` — both scoping dimensions required per spec.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="React 16/17 hooks" location=".claude/patterns/ui/fluent-v9-react-version-boundaries.md">
        Use `useState`, `useMemo`, `useEffect`, `useCallback` — NO `use()`, no React 18-only concurrent features.
      </pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check">Verify context &lt; 60%. If higher, run `context-handoff` before proceeding.</step>
    <step order="0.5" name="Invoke fluent-v9-component">Invoke `Skill fluent-v9-component` (binding per design.md §6.0). Load `fluent-v9-component-authoring.md`, `fluent-v9-theming.md`, `fluent-v9-react-version-boundaries.md`.</step>
    <step order="1" name="Load knowledge">Read ADR-006, ADR-012, ADR-021, ADR-022, ADR-028; load PCF CLAUDE.md. Verify task 050 (FR-BFF-01) is complete — `modifiedAt` + `modifiedBy` must be in `/api/ai/search` projection. Read existing `SemanticSearchControl.tsx`, `ResultsList.tsx`, `ResultCard.tsx`, `types/search.ts`, `services/SemanticSearchApiService.ts`.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Extend search result type">In `types/search.ts`, add `modifiedAt: string` (ISO datetime), `modifiedBy: string` (display name) to the `SearchResult` interface. Update `SemanticSearchApiService.ts` mapping if necessary.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Add view + sort + selection + pin state">In `SemanticSearchControl.tsx`, add state hooks: `view: 'list' | 'card'` (default 'list', hydrated from localStorage), `sortColumn: 'name' | 'modifiedAt' | 'match'` (default 'modifiedAt'), `sortDirection: 'asc' | 'desc'` (default 'desc'), `selection: Set&lt;string&gt;` (set of document IDs), `pinnedIds: Set&lt;string&gt;` (hydrated from localStorage). localStorage keys: `spaarke.docs.view.{userId}.{matterId}`, `spaarke.docs.pinned.{userId}.{matterId}`. Source `userId` from `context.userSettings.userId` and `matterId` from the parent form context.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Implement SortableColumns component">Create `components/SortableColumns.tsx` rendering Fluent v9 `TableHeaderCell` with click handler that toggles asc/desc; sort indicator via `ArrowSortUp20Regular` / `ArrowSortDown20Regular`. Inactive columns show no indicator. Props: `{ columns: ColumnDef[], sortColumn, sortDirection, onSortChange }`.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Implement ListView component">Create `components/ListView.tsx` rendering Fluent v9 `Table` (or `DataGrid`) with columns: Selection checkbox · Pin (icon ONLY when `pinnedIds.has(row.id)`) · Name (file icon + link-styled) · Modified (formatted from `modifiedAt`) · Modified by (avatar + name from `modifiedBy`) · Match (existing score badge) · Three-dot menu (reuses `DocumentRowMenu` from task 040). Apply sort: pinned rows always first, then sort by active column. Row click (excluding menu trigger + checkbox + pin icon) opens `FilePreviewDialog`.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Add view toggle to command bar">In `SemanticSearchControl.tsx`, add the 2-button toggle group to the right end of the command bar. Active button = `appearance="primary"`, inactive = `appearance="subtle"`. Toggling updates state AND writes localStorage immediately.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Wire card view">Card view keeps the existing `ResultsList.tsx` + `ResultCard.tsx` rendering (3-dot menu already wired in task 040). Apply the same sort (pinned first + active column sort) to card grid for consistency.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Pin icon interaction">Click on the pin icon column toggles `pinnedIds.has(row.id)` and writes localStorage. Pin column header is NOT sortable. Use `Pin20Regular` icon, only rendered when pinned.</step>
    <step order="9" name="Selection state persists across view toggles">Verify: select 3 rows in list view → toggle to card view → toggle back to list — selection retained. Selection is in-memory only (not localStorage) for v1.</step>
    <step order="10" name="Dark-mode + a11y check">Run PCF in dev harness with `webLightTheme` and `webDarkTheme`. Verify sortable column headers, checkboxes, pin icons render with v9 tokens. Run axe scan in both themes.</step>
    <step order="11" name="Build verification">Run `npm run build:prod` from PCF root. Verify clean build.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality gates (FULL rigor)">Invoke `Skill code-review` then `Skill adr-check`. Resolve every finding before completion. `code-review` enforces `/fluent-v9-component` invocation.</step>
    <step order="12" name="Checkpoint">Run `context-handoff` (silent: ✅ Checkpoint).</step>
    <step order="13" name="Update task tracking">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 041 status 🔲 → ✅. Reset `current-task.md` to next pending task (likely 042).</step>
  </steps>

